\section{Basic symbols, 187}
\test{%
  \basicsymbolsi   \hfill\mathstrut\penalty0 %
  \basicsymbolsii  \hfill\mathstrut\penalty0 %
  \basicsymbolsiii \hfill\mathstrut\penalty0 %
  \basicsymbolsiv  \hfill\mathstrut\penalty0 %
  \basicsymbolsv
  \text{~Serge\u\i~\t Iur'ev~}% 1
  \straightbraces\lbrace\rbrace % 2
}%
\section{Bold basic symbols, 187}

  \bm\basicsymbolsi   \hfill\mathstrut\penalty0 %

  \bm\basicsymbolsiii \hfill\mathstrut\penalty0 %

  \straightbraces\bm{\lbrace\rbrace}% 2
}%

  \hm\hmpunctuationandothers
}%

  \wwhat\mathem\wwtilde\mathem\wwcheck\mathem

  \straightbraces
  \bigl\{\Bigl\{\biggl\{\Biggl\{\Biggr\}\biggr\}\Bigr\}\bigr\}%
  \morphedbraces
  \bigl\{\Bigl\{\biggl\{\Biggl\{\Biggr\}\biggr\}\Bigr\}\bigr\}%
}%
